# 📝 PRD: ProPDF Editor — Advanced PDF Editing Platform

> **Version:** 1.0  
> **Date:** April 13, 2026  
> **Status:** Draft  
> **Author:** Product Team

---

## 1. 🎯 Vision & Overview

**ProPDF Editor** is a next-generation, browser-based PDF editing platform that goes far beyond what iLovePDF and competitors currently offer. It combines **AI-powered intelligence**, **real-time collaboration**, **advanced design tools**, and a **plugin ecosystem** — delivering a Figma-like experience for PDFs.

### Mission Statement
> *"Make PDF editing as intuitive as Google Docs, as powerful as Photoshop, and as intelligent as an AI assistant."*

---

## 2. 🔍 Competitive Analysis — iLovePDF vs ProPDF Editor

| Feature Area | iLovePDF (Current) | ProPDF Editor (Proposed) |
|---|---|---|
| **Text Editing** | Basic inline text editing | Full rich-text editor with paragraph styles, columns, text wrapping around images |
| **Image Editing** | Insert, resize, rotate | Built-in crop, filters, background removal, AI image enhance |
| **Annotations** | Highlight, underline, draw | Smart annotations with threading, @mentions, reactions, voice notes |
| **Forms** | Basic form fields | Drag-and-drop form builder with conditional logic, validation, calculations |
| **AI Features** | ❌ None | ✅ AI rewrite, translate, summarize, auto-fill, layout suggestions |
| **Collaboration** | ❌ None (single user) | ✅ Real-time multi-user editing with cursors, comments, presence |
| **Version History** | ❌ None | ✅ Full version history with diff view, branching, restore |
| **Templates** | ❌ None | ✅ Template marketplace with 500+ professional templates |
| **Layers** | Basic layer ordering | Advanced layer panel (Photoshop-style) with lock, visibility, grouping |
| **OCR** | Basic OCR (separate tool) | Inline OCR with editable text output + handwriting recognition |
| **Accessibility** | ❌ None | ✅ Auto-tag for WCAG/PDF-UA compliance, screen reader preview |
| **Plugins** | ❌ None | ✅ Plugin marketplace (e-sign, barcode, chart generator, etc.) |
| **Offline Mode** | Desktop app only | PWA with full offline editing + auto-sync |
| **Performance** | Slow on large files | WebAssembly engine, virtual scrolling, 1000+ page support |
| **Redaction** | Basic blackout | AI-powered PII detection + certified redaction with audit log |
| **Export** | PDF only | PDF, PDF/A, PDF/X, DOCX, PPTX, PNG, SVG, HTML |

---

## 3. 👥 Target Users & Personas

### Persona 1: Freelancer (Priya, 28)
- Edits client contracts, invoices, proposals
- Needs: Quick text edits, signatures, beautiful templates
- Pain: iLovePDF is slow, no templates, re-uploads every time

### Persona 2: Legal Professional (Rahul, 42)
- Reviews legal documents, redacts PII, compares document versions
- Needs: Redaction, version history, compliance, collaboration
- Pain: No proper redaction audit trail, no real-time collaboration

### Persona 3: Designer / Marketer (Sarah, 31)
- Creates brochures, reports, presentations in PDF
- Needs: Advanced layout tools, image editing, brand consistency
- Pain: Has to jump between Canva, Word, and iLovePDF

### Persona 4: Enterprise Team (TechCorp, 500+ employees)
- Company-wide PDF workflows (HR forms, reports, compliance docs)
- Needs: SSO, team management, templates, API, audit logs
- Pain: No centralized PDF tool with governance features

